    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134990/extras/71bf45de77415cf292bee05acf3100d9.avif?t=1732219125\" width=650 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is time to use your <i>fabulous fashion skills</i> to dress up <strong>THAT</strong> fish and make it look <i>breathtaking!!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Browse through our wardrobe of <strong>100+ cosmetics</strong> and select the best pieces to make your <i>unique outfit!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134990/extras/6cae8d6e77674fb31c4bacac13eb28f2.avif?t=1732219125\" width=650 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use our editing tools to adjust each item to make sure it fits perfectly to your design! Use <strong>Scale</strong>, <strong>Rotation</strong>, <strong>Layering</strong> and <strong>change the colour</strong> of nearly any item!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134990/extras/ab2a01c14b6924c3b2e823a77969f847.avif?t=1732219125\" width=650 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easily <strong>take pictures or create stickers</strong> (without background!) to easily <strong>share with anyone!</strong></p>",
